DNR Worthy of repost OilspillMay 29th 836 pmDNR The way we have phrased our company message is that we have set a general threshold of remaining profitable at 50 for sanctioning projects a longterm basis Thats not to say the Company cannot survive for periods below that price and we have proven it in the past oil was as low as 26 since 2015 Obviously our costs just to produce are lower than that but it gives a better indication of what we see longerterm Clearly we are not up against any maturities today and are generating free cash flow and staying within our debt covenants Best Regards John John A Mayer Director of SEC Reporting Investor Relations
